00 178w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=125,70 125w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=600,338 600w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=660,370 660w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=1280,720 1280w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=1000,563 1000w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=910,511 910w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=681,383 681w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=450,253 450w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=250,140 250w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=296,166 296w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=248,139 248w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=200,112 200w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=270,152 270w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=60,34 60w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=352,198 352w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=110,62 110w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=285,160 285w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=320,180 320w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=640,360 640w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-GAR-RUNDT-OG-FORELSKER-SIG_still_04_swe_-2.png?resize=800,450 800w\"/\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003eL-R Lars Hammar, Fredrik Wikingsson, and Lars Hammar drive to France in ‘The Last Journey’\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ccite\u003eNexiko\u003c/cite\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\t“I’ve known Filip’s dad for as long as I’ve known Filip — since the mid ‘90s, and I’ve loved him since I got to know him,” Wikingsson added. “I saw the gradual decline, if you want to call it that, of [Lars] just sitting at home. Filip told me, ‘I want to do something for my dad, desperately,’ and we spitballed, ‘What could that be?’ Then when he started talking about, ‘Maybe I should get an old Renault 4 from the ‘70s [the kind of vehicle the Hammar family had driven on their summer excursions to the Riviera] and then we started getting [mental] images of that little car going through Europe, it seems a little cinematic. That would be interesting to maybe tell that story and see if other people can be touched by it.”\n\n\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\tLars was not a particularly eager participant at the start of the journey and within hours of leaving home he had taken a spill, breaking some bones.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\t“I’m in pain and uncertain how this will go,” Lars confides in a video diary. Once ambulatory again, the trip resumed and as the trio of Lars, Filip, and Fredrik crossed into France, Lars’s spirits showed occasional signs of revivifying. A Francophile \u003cem\u003epar excellence\u003c/em\u003e, somehow the ways of the French never failed to delight him – probably because of the contrast to comparatively buttoned-down Swedish culture.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\n\t“Every Frenchman is a tiny president!” he says admiringly at one point in the film.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?w=300\" data-lazy-src=\"https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?w=300\" alt=\"Father and son: Filip Hammar (left) with his dad Lars in \u0026#39;The Last Journey\u0026#39;\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png 3840w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=150,84 150w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=300,169 300w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=2048,1152 2048w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=178,100 178w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=125,70 125w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/10541_ALLE-MAND-PA-DAEK_still_05_swe_.png?resize=600,338 600w, https://deadline.com/wp-content/u